Package: calc-interest
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple interest calculator
 Reads principal, annual rate, and number of periods from standard input
 and writes the computed simple interest and total repayment amount to
 standard output. No network access; no configuration files.
